<h1>Tutorial: Create your own Theme</h1>

<h2>Create your own Style theme</h2>

<p>
  Simply copy the default theme and modify how you want it:
</p>
<pre>
cp -r src/themes/styles/default src/themes/styles/mytheme
edit src/themes/styles/mytheme/metadata.json
edit src/themes/styles/mytheme/style.less
edit src/conf/112-themes.json # Or http://os.js.org/doc/manuals/man-configuration.html
grunt config themes:styles:mytheme
</pre>
<p>
  Then update the theme manifest and LESS manually
</p>

