<h2>Create your own Font theme</h2>
<p>
  Just add your fonts in a sub-folder like <b>Karla</b>. Then update the included stylesheet with correct name(s).
</p>
<pre>
edit src/conf/112-themes.json # Or http://os.js.org/doc/manuals/man-configuration.html
grunt config themes:fonts
</pre>


<h1>Update your changes</h1>
<p>
  Just run the same grunt commands as when you created the themes :)
</p>
